reviewText: This isn't USA region coding, but it works just fine in universal DVD players. It is region 2 (PAL), so make sure your device is compatible or else it will not work. As far as the series, it's interesting seeing this family at the beginning of their show. They play the most recent four seasons over and over again on tv. The Kardashian and Jenners have grown so much since then. What a difference!
The DVDs don't work. I'm pissed.
Omg I love the Kardashians! So hilaro and great DVD set!  Region free DVD player only!
When Im super bored or in need of some drama, I pop KUWTK in the dvd player and get my dose. Too bad they don't have a huge pack with all the seasons, I'd definitely buy it!
